i => for insert mode
esc => command mode
:   => last line mode
:w  => write or save
j,k down,up
h,l left,right
:q  => quit or exit
:q! => without saving
:wq => save and quit
p  => paste the line
dd => delete a line
yy => copy a line
u  => for undo
ctr + r => for redo
d5d => delete 5 lines
y4y => copy 4 line
/test search for test keyword
n => next ( next find )
N => ( previous find )
x => to delete a single char 

vimtutor => to learn advanced vim
